title.rendered: TTE gets awarded by Johnson Controls-Hitachi

content.rendered: TTE’s Products & Solutions division recently received an award from partners Johnson Controls–Hitachi Air Conditioning for Outstanding Sales Performance in the fiscal year 2022. Nada Tadros, Regional Sales Manager, Johnson Controls Hitachi visited TTE headquarters to present the trophy to Dilip Sharma, Executive Vice President, TTE, Roshan Samuel, Vice President, TTE – Products & Solutions and the executive sales team.
